---
title: Crispy Chickpea and Roasted Cauliflower Salad with Quinoa and Roasted Garlic Vinaigrette
description: Cauliflower is one of the most versatile veggies out there. You can mash it, steam it, eat it raw, or—our personal favorite—roast it. In this recipe, we throw it in the oven with crispy chickpeas and carrots before tossing everything together with hearty quinoa.
